{"code":"#include <iostream>\n\nusing namespace std;\n\nenum Flag { NORMAL, NAN, INF };\n\n\nclass Fraction\n\n{\npublic:\n  double convert( Flag & flag )\n@你的代码\n\n \n\n  \n\n};\nint main()\n\n{\n\n    int num;    // 分子\n\n    int den;    // 分母\n\n \n\n    // 依次输入分子、分母\n\n    cin >> num >> den;\n\n \n\n    Fraction z;\n\n    z.assign( num, den );\n\n    cout << \"z = \";\n\n    z.print();\n\n \n\n    Flag flag;\n\n    double val = z.convert(flag);\n\n \n\n    switch(flag)\n\n    {\n\n    case NORMAL:\n\n        cout << \" = \" << val << endl;\n\n        break;\n\n    case NAN:\n\n        cout << \" = #NAN\" << endl;\n\n        break;\n\n    case INF:\n\n        cout << \" = #INF\" << endl;\n\n        break;\n\n    default:\n\n        break;\n\n    }\n\n \n\n    z.invert();\n\n    cout << \"1/z = \";\n\n    z.print();\n\n    cout << endl;\n\n   \n\n    return 0;\n\n}\n\n ","content":"<p class=\"a\" style=\"margin: 6pt 0cm 3pt 18pt\"><font class=\"Apple-style-span\" face=\"'Times New Roman'\"><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"font-size: medium;\"> </span></font></p>\n<p class=\"a\">【问题描述】</p>\n<p class=\"a\"><font class=\"Apple-style-span\" face=\"'Times New Roman'\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><span style=\"mso-list:Ignore\"><span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">实现一个表示分数的</span><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Fraction</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">类。在该类中有两个数据成员分别用于存储分数的分子和分母。函数成员中包含一个设置分子和分母的函数</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">assign()</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">，转换成</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">double </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">类型数值的函数</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">convert()</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">，交换分子和分母的函数</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">invert()</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">以及一个输出分数的函数</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">print()</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">，请<span style=\"color:red\">注意输出结果格式</span>：若分子分母同时为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">0</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">，则输出字符串&ldquo;</span><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:red\">#NAN</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&rdquo;；若只有分母为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">0</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">，则输出字符串&ldquo;</span><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:red\">#INF</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&rdquo;；其余情况输出最简分式，即<span style=\"color:red\">最大公因子</span>已被约去后的形式；当分子为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">0</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">，分母为负数时，注意结果应输出</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">0</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">，而非&ldquo;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">-0</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&rdquo;。</span></font></p>\n<p><font class=\"Apple-style-span\" face=\"'Times New Roman'\"> </font></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><font class=\"Apple-style-span\" face=\"'Times New Roman'\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></font></p>\n<p><font class=\"Apple-style-span\" face=\"'Times New Roman'\"> </font></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:18.0pt\"><font class=\"Apple-style-span\" face=\"'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\nbackground:#D9D9D9;mso-shading:white;mso-pattern:gray-15 auto\">第一步</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">：首先通过枚举类型</span><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Flag</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">来定义表示分值求值结果的状态，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:red\">NORMAL</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">表示两个非零数相除，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:red\">NAN</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">表示分子分母同时为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">0</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:red\">INF</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">表示分子不为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">0</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">而分母为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">0</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">。</span></font></p>\n<p><font class=\"Apple-style-span\" face=\"'Times New Roman'\"> </font></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-left:21.0pt;mso-para-margin-left:\n2.0gd;text-align:left;background:#F2F2F2;mso-background-themecolor:background1;\nmso-background-themeshade:242;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\"><font class=\"Apple-style-span\" face=\"'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp;</font></p>\n<p><font class=\"Apple-style-span\" face=\"'Times New Roman'\"> </font></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:18.0pt\"><font class=\"Apple-style-span\" face=\"'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\nbackground:#D9D9D9;mso-shading:white;mso-pattern:gray-15 auto\">第二步</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">：依据题意实现</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Fraction</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">类。</span></font></p>\n<p><font class=\"Apple-style-span\" face=\"'Times New Roman'\"> </font></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-left:21.0pt;mso-para-margin-left:\n2.0gd;text-align:left;background:#F2F2F2;mso-background-themecolor:background1;\nmso-background-themeshade:242;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\"><font class=\"Apple-style-span\" face=\"'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp;</font></p>\n<p><font class=\"Apple-style-span\" face=\"'Times New Roman'\"> </font></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:18.0pt\"><font class=\"Apple-style-span\" face=\"'Times New Roman'\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></font></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; text-indent: 18pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\nbackground:#D9D9D9;mso-shading:white;mso-pattern:gray-15 auto\">第三步</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">：依据下列测试程序对所编写的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Fraction</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">类进行测试。</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; text-indent: 18pt;\">【输入样例1】</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; margin-left: 21pt; text-align: left; background-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">0 -100<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-left: 21pt; text-align: left; background-color: rgb(242, 242, 242);\"><font color=\"#ff0000\" face=\"宋体\">【输出样例1】</font></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; margin-left: 21pt; text-align: left; background-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">z = 0/-1 = 0<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; margin-left: 21pt; text-align: left; background-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">1/z = -1/0<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-left: 21pt; text-align: left; background-color: rgb(242, 242, 242);\"><font face=\"宋体\">【输入样例2】</font></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; margin-left: 21pt; text-align: left; background-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">100 0<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-left: 21pt; text-align: left; background-color: rgb(242, 242, 242);\"><font color=\"#ff0000\" face=\"宋体\">【输出样例2】</font></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; margin-left: 21pt; text-align: left; background-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">z = 1/0 = #INF<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; margin-left: 21pt; text-align: left; background-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">1/z = 0/1<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-left: 21pt; text-align: left; background-color: rgb(242, 242, 242);\"><font face=\"宋体\">【输入样例1】</font></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; margin-left: 21pt; text-align: left; background-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">24 -36<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-left: 21pt; text-align: left; background-color: rgb(242, 242, 242);\"><font color=\"#ff0000\" face=\"宋体\">【输出样例1】</font></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; margin-left: 21pt; text-align: left; background-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">z = 2/-3 = -0.666667<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; margin-left: 21pt; text-align: left; background-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">1/z = -3/2<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; margin-left: 21pt; text-align: left; background-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span id=\"1301055624653S\" style=\"display: none\">&nbsp;</span></p>","fcontent":"<div class='pdsec'>问题描述</div><div class='pdcont'>　　实现一个表示分数的<b>Fraction</b>类。在该类中有两个数据成员分别用于存储分数的分子和分母。函数成员中包含一个设置分子和分母的函数assign()，转换成double 类型数值的函数convert()，交换分子和分母的函数invert()以及一个输出分数的函数print()，请注意输出结果格式：若分子分母同时为0，则输出字符串“<b>#NAN</b>”；若只有分母为0，则输出字符串“<b>#INF</b>”；其余情况输出最简分式，即最大公因子已被约去后的形式；当分子为0，分母为负数时，注意结果应输出0，而非“-0”。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n　　第一步：首先通过枚举类型<b>Flag</b>来定义表示分值求值结果的状态，NORMAL表示两个非零数相除，NAN表示分子分母同时为0，INF表示分子不为0而分母为0。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n　　第二步：依据题意实现Fraction类。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n　　第三步：依据下列测试程序对所编写的Fraction类进行测试。</div><div class='pdsec'>样例输入</div><div class='pddata'>0 -100</div><div class='pdsec'>样例输出</div><div class='pddata'>z = 0/-1 = 0<br />\n1/z = -1/0</div><div class='pdsec'>样例输入</div><div class='pddata'>100 0</div><div class='pdsec'>样例输出</div><div class='pddata'>z = 1/0 = #INF<br />\n1/z = 0/1</div><div class='pdsec'>样例输入</div><div class='pddata'>24 -36</div><div class='pdsec'>样例输出</div><div class='pddata'>z = 2/-3 = -0.666667<br />\n1/z = -3/2</div>\n","files":"","gpid":"D5674","indatacount":0,"inputfile":"","langs":"CPP","memorylimit":"32.0MB","opid":0,"outputfile":"","remain":0,"ret":1,"specialjudge":"","src":"","subinter":0,"timelimit":"2.0s","title":"c++_ch04_03","type":"DEFAULT"}